title: Forgotten Lair of the Silent General
story: For years the lair of the Silent General was considered lost. Recently a band of cultists rediscovered it. The lair of the Silent General is home to a valuable specie of plants.

notes.text: A bald gnome, sleeping on the ground.
A dying bard, some gold among his belongings.
An intricate puzzle, puts a person to sleep when solved.
A large iron gate on the southern wall of the small room.
A mosaic of a heart pattern on the floor
